title: aflake
name: aflake
description: This data set is derived from sample data distributed with ArcGIS Desktop. It represents the water features (freshwater and ocean) in the Horn of Africa (northeastern region) at a map scale of 1:3 million.  This dataset is clipped from the water coverage in ESRI's ArcWorld Supplement data product. It was created for instructional use with ESRI software training modules or for demonstration and should not be used or relied on for other purposes.
